-- Trafigura Close to Deal to Invest in Thamesteel, Times Reports
-- B y   T u h i n   K a r
-- 2012-01-22T12:59:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-22/trafigura-close-to-deal-to-invest-in-thamesteel-times-reports.html
Trafigura is close to a deal to
invest in Thamesteel Ltd. without buying a stake in the U.K.
steel mill, the Sunday Times reported, without saying where it
got the information.  Due diligence on the mill, owned by Saudi Al-Tuwairqi
Group, may be near completion, according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
